Class userData

  • Constructor Details

    • userData

      public userData​(int rating, String notes, int day, int month, String localdate)
      userData constructs a new userData object.
      Parameters:
      rating - The rating the user gives to the day which is a value ranging from 1-10.
      notes - The notes are specific things that the user has about a given day.
      day - A number 0-30 which defines the day of the month.
      month - A number 0-11 which defines the month of the year.
      localdate - A string containing the day, month, and year.
